SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       The full documentation for ssuumm is maintained as
       a Texinfo  manual.   If the iinnffoo and ssuumm
       programs are properly installed at your site, the
       com‐ mand

              iinnffoo ssuumm

       should give you access to the complete manual.



